sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects process command line patterns and locations used by REvil group in Kaseya incident (can also match on other malware)
Detects the execution of an executable that is typically used by PlugX for DLL side loading starting from an uncommon location

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Use Short Name Path in Command Line
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detect use of the Windows 8.3 short name. Which could be used as a method to avoid command-line detection
